T*
(pausing options, plan changes, and refund eligibility specific to subscriptions.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(1. AVAILABLE SUBSCRIPTION PLANS) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.1 Basic Plan) Tj
T*
(Monthly fee: $9.99/month or $99.99/year \(save 17%\)) Tj
T*
(Includes: Free standard shipping on every order, early access to select sales, and 5%) Tj
T*
(cashback on purchases applied as store credit.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.2 Premium Plan) Tj
T*
(Monthly fee: $19.99/month or $199.99/year \(save 17%\)) Tj
T*
(Includes everything in Basic, plus: Free expedited shipping on orders over $35,) Tj
T*
(priority customer support, access to members-only flash deals, extended 60-day) Tj
T*
(returns, and 10% cashback on purchases.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.3 Family Plan) Tj
T*
(Monthly fee: $29.99/month or $299.99/year \(save 17%\)) Tj
T*
(Includes everything in Premium, plus: Up to 5 linked accounts, shared membership) Tj
T*
(benefits across all linked accounts, and 12% cashback.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
