T*
(Custom pricing based on usage volume and team size. Includes all Premium benefits, a) Tj
T*
(dedicated account manager, consolidated invoicing, and tax-exempt purchasing options.) Tj
T*
(Contact enterprise@shopexample.com for a quote.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(2. BILLING AND PAYMENT) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2.1 Billing Cycle) Tj
T*
(Monthly plans renew automatically every 30 days from the date of initial purchase.) Tj
T*
(Annual plans renew automatically 12 months from the date of initial purchase. Your) Tj
T*
(billing date is the same calendar date each month \(or year\) as when you first) Tj
T*
(subscribed. For example, if you subscribed on January 15, you will be billed on) Tj
T*
(February 15, March 15, and so on.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2.2 Payment Methods Accepted) Tj
T*
(- Credit and debit cards \(Visa, Mastercard, American Express, Discover\)) Tj
