(2.3 Automatic Renewal) Tj
T*
(Subscriptions renew automatically to ensure uninterrupted service. We will send a) Tj
T*
(renewal reminder email 7 days before your annual renewal date. Monthly renewals do) Tj
T*
(not generate a pre-renewal email, but you will receive a receipt after each renewal) Tj
T*
(charge.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2.4 Failed Payment) Tj
T*
(If a subscription payment fails, we will:) Tj
T*
(- Retry the charge after 3 days) Tj
T*
(- Retry again after 7 days) Tj
T*
(- Notify you by email after each failed attempt with instructions to update your) Tj
T*
(payment method) Tj
T*
(- Suspend your subscription if payment fails after 10 days from the original due date) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(During a payment failure grace period \(up to 10 days\), your subscription benefits) Tj
T*
(remain active. If your subscription is suspended due to non-payment, you can) Tj
T*
(reactivate it at any time by updating your payment method ? your billing cycle) Tj
T*
(restarts from the date of reactivation.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2.5 Price Changes) Tj
T*
(We reserve the right to change subscription pricing. We will notify you at least 30) Tj
T*
(days in advance of any price increase via email. The new price takes effect at your) Tj
T*
(next renewal date following the notice period. If you do not agree with the new) Tj
T*
(pricing, you may cancel before the renewal date at no charge.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(3. MANAGING YOUR SUBSCRIPTION) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.1 Accessing Subscription Settings) Tj
T*
(Log into your account and go to Account > Subscriptions to:) Tj
T*
(- View your current plan and billing date) Tj
T*
(- Update your payment method) Tj
T*
(- Upgrade or downgrade your plan) Tj
T*
(- Pause your subscription) Tj
T*
(- Cancel your subscription) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.2 Updating Payment Information) Tj
T*
(You can update your payment method at any time in Account > Subscriptions > Payment) Tj
T*
(Method. Changes take effect immediately and are used for the next renewal charge.) Tj
T*
(Your existing billing cycle is not affected.) Tj
T*
() Tj
