T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6.1 How to Cancel) Tj
T*
(You can cancel at any time through Account > Subscriptions > Cancel. Cancellation) Tj
T*
(takes effect at the end of the current billing period ? there is no charge for) Tj
T*
(cancelling, and you retain full benefits until your period ends.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6.2 Cancellation for Annual Plans) Tj
T*
(If you cancel an annual plan, your benefits remain active through the end of the paid) Tj
T*
(annual period. No prorated refund is provided for unused months of an annual plan,) Tj
T*
(except during the initial refund window \(see Section 7\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6.3 Cancellation Confirmation) Tj
T*
(You will receive a cancellation confirmation email immediately. If you do not receive) Tj
T*
(this email within a few minutes, check your spam folder. If you still do not receive) Tj
T*
(it, contact support ? do not assume the cancellation was processed.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6.4 Re-subscribing After Cancellation) Tj
T*
(You can re-subscribe at any time after cancellation by visiting Account >) Tj
T*
(Subscriptions. If you re-subscribe within 30 days of cancellation, your original) Tj
T*
(billing date and any loyalty progress may be restored.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(7. REFUND POLICY FOR SUBSCRIPTIONS) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.1 New Subscription Refund Window) Tj
T*
(For new subscriptions \(first-time subscribers\), a full refund is available within 7) Tj
T*
(days of the initial charge if you have not used any subscription benefits \(e.g., free) Tj
T*
(shipping, cashback redemption, or priority support access\). Contact) Tj
T*
(support@shopexample.com to request this refund.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.2 Renewal Refunds) Tj
T*
(Refunds for subscription renewals are available within 7 days of the renewal charge) Tj
T*
(if you have not used any benefits since the renewal date. This is available once per) Tj
T*
(12-month period per account.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.3 No Prorated Refunds) Tj
T*
(We do not provide prorated refunds for partially used subscription periods outside of) Tj
T*
(the 7-day windows described above. If you cancel on day 15 of a 30-day cycle, your) Tj
T*
(benefits remain active through day 30, but no refund is issued for the unused 15) Tj
T*
(days.) Tj
